en.definition:
The process of locking cryptocurrency to support blockchain network operations in [?-Proof of Stake-]{Alternative to mining, more energy-efficient} systems.

Stakers are rewarded for [?-validating transactions-]{Confirming that transactions are legitimate} and maintaining network security.

**Benefits:**
- Earn [?-passive income-]{Regular rewards for holding and staking your crypto}
- More energy-efficient than mining
- Supports network [?-decentralization-]{Distribution of power across many participants}

A popular [?-browser extension-]{Plugin that adds functionality to your web browser} and mobile app that functions as an Ethereum wallet and gateway to blockchain applications.

**Features:**
- Store and manage Ethereum and [?-ERC-20 tokens-]{Tokens built on the Ethereum blockchain following a standard}
- Interact with dApps directly from your browser
- Secure [?-key management-]{Safely stores your private keys locally}
- [?-Multi-network support-]{Connect to different blockchains and test networks}

zh.definition:
一款流行的[?-浏览器扩展-]{为网页浏览器添加功能的插件}和移动应用，作为以太坊钱包和区块链应用网关。

**功能：**
- 存储和管理以太币及[?-ERC-20代币-]{遵循标准在以太坊区块链上构建的代币}
- 直接从浏览器与dApp交互
- 安全[?-密钥管理-]{在本地安全存储您的私钥}
- [?-多网络支持-]{连接到不同的区块链和测试网络}

在[?-权益证明-]{挖矿的替代方案，更节能}系统中锁定加密货币以支持区块链网络运营的过程。

质押者因[?-验证交易-]{确认交易是否合法}和维护网络安全而获得奖励。

**优势：**
- 赚取[?-被动收入-]{通过持有和质押加密货币获得定期奖励}
- 比挖矿更节能
- 支持网络[?-去中心化-]{权力在众多参与者之间分配}
